(1, 6, 11, 'Bersama Mewujudkan Generasi Qurani yang Mandiri dan Berakhlak Mulia', 'Homepage', '<p>Bersama PESANTREN AL HIKAMUSSALAFIE, kami berkomitmen menghadirkan pendidikan berbasis Al-Qur\'an guna membentuk generasi Qurani yang berakhlak mulia, mandiri, serta siap meniadi pemimpin masa depan.</p>', '1773156020_5cd646e575140256d79e.png', 'https://haqi.sch.id', 'Lihat detail', 11, 'Tidak', '2022-12-08 04:04:01', '2026-03-10 15:20:20'),
(2, 6, 11, 'Workshop Digital Marketing di Java Web Media', 'Galeri', '<p>Video provides a powerful way to help you prove your point. When you click Online Video, you can paste in the embed code for the video you want to add. You can also type a keyword to search online for the video that best fits your document.</p>', '1773057137_78bf971cb8adaaec4ed3.jpg', 'https://youtu.be/RZSBYMtwyDo?si=TDW3ztLAkiB4r6bn', 'Lihat detail', 3, 'Ya', '2023-05-01 19:05:56', '2026-03-10 15:02:14'),
